EqlLldpV2ChassisIdSubtype.name: EqlLldpV2ChassisIdSubtype
EqlLldpV2ChassisIdSubtype.description: This describes the source of a chassis identifier.

EqlLldpV2ChassisId.name: EqlLldpV2ChassisId
EqlLldpV2ChassisId.description: This describes the format of a chassis identifier string.

EqlLldpV2PortIdSubtype.name: EqlLldpV2PortIdSubtype
EqlLldpV2PortIdSubtype.description: This describes the source of a particular type of port identifier used in the LLDP MIB.

EqlLldpV2PortId.name: EqlLldpV2PortId
EqlLldpV2PortId.description: This describes the format of a port identifier string.

EqlLldpV2State.name: EqlLldpV2State
EqlLldpV2State.description: This describes the state of LLDP for the port.

eqlLldpDynamicIfTable.name: eqlLldpDynamicIfTable
eqlLldpDynamicIfTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic A table of LLDP information per each interface of a system. Each row in this table supplies values for one port's LLDP parameters.

eqlLldpDynamicIfEntry.name: eqlLldpDynamicIfEntry
eqlLldpDynamicIfEntry.description: An entry in the LLDP table, containing information about LLDP on a single interface.

eqlLldpRemMacAddress.name: eqlLldpRemMacAddress
eqlLldpRemMacAddress.description: The MAC address associated with the LLDP peer.

eqlLldpV2RemChassisIdSubtype.name: eqlLldpV2RemChassisIdSubtype
eqlLldpV2RemChassisIdSubtype.description: The type of encoding used to identify the chassis associated with the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemChassisId.name: eqlLldpV2RemChassisId
eqlLldpV2RemChassisId.description: The string value used to identify the chassis component associated with the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemPortIdSubtype.name: eqlLldpV2RemPortIdSubtype
eqlLldpV2RemPortIdSubtype.description: The type of encoding used to identify the port associated with the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemPortId.name: eqlLldpV2RemPortId
eqlLldpV2RemPortId.description: The string value used to identify the port component associated with the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemPortDesc.name: eqlLldpV2RemPortDesc
eqlLldpV2RemPortDesc.description: The string value used to identify the description of the given port associated with the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemSysName.name: eqlLldpV2RemSysName
eqlLldpV2RemSysName.description: The string value used to identify the system name of the remote system.

eqlLldpV2RemSysDesc.name: eqlLldpV2RemSysDesc
eqlLldpV2RemSysDesc.description: The string value used to identify the system description of the remote system.

eqlLldpV2State.name: eqlLldpV2State
eqlLldpV2State.description: The current LLDP state for the port.

eqlLldpV2RemMgmtAddr.name: eqlLldpV2RemMgmtAddr
eqlLldpV2RemMgmtAddr.description: The management address reported by the remote system. If multiple addresses were reported, they are delimited by commas.
